  "detailed_description": "<h1>Wishlist Tentacular!</h1><p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1220100/extras/2c0dc9a9afdc51ebc40e0220687d904a.poster.avif?t=1734614548\" width=600 height=82 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1220100/extras/2c0dc9a9afdc51ebc40e0220687d904a.webm?t=1734614548\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1220100/extras/2c0dc9a9afdc51ebc40e0220687d904a.mp4?t=1734614548\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1220100/extras/f3a2e27af2e3b7558339c7710f2f1281.poster.avif?t=1734614548\" width=600 height=116 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1220100/extras/f3a2e27af2e3b7558339c7710f2f1281.webm?t=1734614548\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1220100/extras/f3a2e27af2e3b7558339c7710f2f1281.mp4?t=1734614548\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Discuss secrets, solutions or give feedback.. We’re always looking for players who want to playtest new features. </p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Ten out of Tentacles!</h2>INKredible physics allowing you to fulfill your squid dreams.<br>Inhabit the giant body of a mighty-yet-mild tentacle monster raised by the quirky townsfolk of La Kalma, a remote island colony packed with puzzles.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1220100/extras/57cef17c84056530e18c85c60572e915.poster.avif?t=1734614548\" width=704 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1220100/extras/57cef17c84056530e18c85c60572e915.webm?t=1734614548\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1220100/extras/57cef17c84056530e18c85c60572e915.mp4?t=1734614548\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Kraken your brain with 60+ mind bending puzzles</h2>Tentacular is a heart-warming physics-based puzzler bursting with inventive, immersive gameplay and lots of humor to boot. Solve puzzles using playful tools to build strange contraptions and spectacular structures, or wreak havoc with your lumbering bulk!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1220100/extras/7490ec0f25b63be1584b8733a55ab3e8.poster.avif?t=1734614548\" width=704 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1220100/extras/7490ec0f25b63be1584b8733a55ab3e8.webm?t=1734614548\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1220100/extras/7490ec0f25b63be1584b8733a55ab3e8.mp4?t=1734614548\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Enjoy a lengthy VR story experience with a playtime of over 10 hours</h2>Experience a sweet and funny adventure about figuring out where you came from, and where you belong. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1220100/extras/90d0fab1164faade9661b401ab9010f1.poster.avif?t=1734614548\" width=704 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1220100/extras/90d0fab1164faade9661b401ab9010f1.webm?t=1734614548\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1220100/extras/90d0fab1164faade9661b401ab9010f1.mp4?t=1734614548\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >INKubate incredible towns with the brand new Island Builder Expansion</h2>Build your ultimate island in the brand new Island Builder Expansion – free for all Tentacular owners!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1220100/extras/9283550b93a3b11a6878efa313837d68.poster.avif?t=1734614548\" width=704 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1220100/extras/9283550b93a3b11a6878efa313837d68.webm?t=1734614548\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1220100/extras/9283550b93a3b11a6878efa313837d68.mp4?t=1734614548\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1220100/extras/e175dc0fa64eee3684d9cbe6f2c66054.avif?t=1734614548\" width=600 height=300 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Ten out of Tentacles!</h2>INKredible physics allowing you to fulfill your squid dreams.<br>Inhabit the giant body of a mighty-yet-mild tentacle monster raised by the quirky townsfolk of La Kalma, a remote island colony packed with puzzles.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1220100/extras/57cef17c84056530e18c85c60572e915.poster.avif?t=1734614548\" width=704 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1220100/extras/57cef17c84056530e18c85c60572e915.webm?t=1734614548\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1220100/extras/57cef17c84056530e18c85c60572e915.mp4?t=1734614548\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Kraken your brain with 60+ mind bending puzzles</h2>Tentacular is a heart-warming physics-based puzzler bursting with inventive, immersive gameplay and lots of humor to boot. Solve puzzles using playful tools to build strange contraptions and spectacular structures, or wreak havoc with your lumbering bulk!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1220100/extras/7490ec0f25b63be1584b8733a55ab3e8.poster.avif?t=1734614548\" width=704 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1220100/extras/7490ec0f25b63be1584b8733a55ab3e8.webm?t=1734614548\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1220100/extras/7490ec0f25b63be1584b8733a55ab3e8.mp4?t=1734614548\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Enjoy a lengthy VR story experience with a playtime of over 10 hours</h2>Experience a sweet and funny adventure about figuring out where you came from, and where you belong. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1220100/extras/90d0fab1164faade9661b401ab9010f1.poster.avif?t=1734614548\" width=704 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1220100/extras/90d0fab1164faade9661b401ab9010f1.webm?t=1734614548\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1220100/extras/90d0fab1164faade9661b401ab9010f1.mp4?t=1734614548\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >INKubate incredible towns with the brand new Island Builder Expansion</h2>Build your ultimate island in the brand new Island Builder Expansion – free for all Tentacular owners!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1220100/extras/9283550b93a3b11a6878efa313837d68.poster.avif?t=1734614548\" width=704 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1220100/extras/9283550b93a3b11a6878efa313837d68.webm?t=1734614548\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1220100/extras/9283550b93a3b11a6878efa313837d68.mp4?t=1734614548\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1220100/extras/e175dc0fa64eee3684d9cbe6f2c66054.avif?t=1734614548\" width=600 height=300 /></span>",
